The Kingsmen and Gold City put on such an awesome performance. I remember listening to the Kingsmen as a child and some of the songs were on the tape I had back then. This is a must have IF your a Kingsmen fan.
The DVD would not play the songs all the way through

I was very happy with the prompt well protected wrapped CD and DVD I got as a gift for a loved one that had the old cassets and had no way to listen to then .
This was a great find for the perfect gift and arrived in time even with the Christmas rush.

I got this for my dad for Christmas along with Vol 1. I grew up going to New Years Eve sings with him and mom and we listened to both the Kingsmen and Gold City. These two groups have a lot of fun together while lifting up the Lord's name. The quality of transfer to DVD was much better than I expected.
This dvd showcases a lot of good southern gospel talent.  These two groups sound great together and we enjoyed it very much.  Good buy for the money.  :)

I was impressed with this product. I couldn't find it anywhere else so I was very happy when I saw it. If you like the good old southern gospel music its definitely a good buy!! It even has Old Jim Hamill in it.
